All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
Division
This Class creates an instance of a division with user input information includes getters and setters to edit information from other classes.
DivisionList
The DivisionList class constructs and adds functionality to the division arrayList.
Scout
This Class creates an instance of a scout with user input information and assigns the scout to a division.
ScoutingSystem
The ScoutingSystem class acts as the user interface.
ScoutList
The ScoutList class contains methods which can be called in the ScoutingSystem class to interact with and add functionality to the arrayList of scouts
